org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.codegen.databinding

Class WatcherInfoBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.codegen.databinding.WatcherInfoBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FunctionWatcherInfo, PropertyWatcherInfo, XMLWatcherInfo

    public class WatcherInfoBase
extends Object
    base class for the different watcher info classes Contains all the information needed to CG an mx.binding.Watcher object There is a one to one relationship between instances of this class, and Flex Watcher objects that will be created at runtime This class has two purposes: The main one it to provide a convenient way for the derived classes to inherit functionality In some cases, also used as a polymorphic case class.
